New Records: Ruben Trumpelmann bagged four wickets, including two with his first two balls
Key Match Events: David Wiese successfully defended a 22-run target in the super over
Namibia skittled Oman for 109 all out in 19.4 overs
Miscellaneous Highlights: Namibia defeated Oman after the thrilling match entered a super over
